ProcessEntity.Note: This process is to encapsulate the common functionality required Phases and or components that need to have an understanding of multiple products. and provide navigation components for those products at Process Level.

This Process is for encapsulating single account based processing e.g. StandingOrders for an account or Upcoming payments for an account.

 

The responsibility of each component phase to to make use of a top navigation and account cards as they see fit. By not including those elements at process level we dont impose a potentially restrictive design paradigm.
